Having made promises to keep his fans glued to his music and remain relevant in the Nigerian music industry, popular comedian cum singer, Mutolib Ottan famously known as Tolibian, appears to be keeping to his words by releasing hit songs to the delight of his fans. The singer broke the airwaves with his song, ‘Abaya palava’ in 2021 which has recorded huge listenership on digital streaming platforms. Following the success of the song he recently released a remake version of the song, ‘Abaya remix’ featuring popular female singer, Raybekah which is also currently being played on all platforms. Tolibian continues to show his determination to achieve his goals of being one of the most sought-after artistes in the industry with the release of his new sound entitled ‘Neighbour’. The singer said he aims to make his name known and unforgettable in the music world, adding that he is up to the task of becoming an unforgettable name when it comes to music in Nigeria and Africa at large. “I’m ever ready to keep to my words; I want my music to be heard in Nigeria and in the diaspora. I’m excited about my progress lately because I am achieving my goals that I’ve set – one hit at a time. The song Neighbour is just a prelude to what I have in store for my fans this year,” he said. Tolibian is currently under the management of Dami Adenuga’s DAW Empire. ORITAMEFA BAPTIST MODEL SCHOOLS, (OBMS), IBADAN 
